{
  "id": "adv_main_01_06_01",
  "title": "星見編2章16話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（さくら達サニーピースと、琴乃達月のテンペストが）\n（同時デビューを果たしてから一週間が経った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s been one week since Sakura’s group‚ Sunny Peace‚ and Kotono’s group‚ Moon Tempest)\n(made their joint debut.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（上々の滑り出しだったが、問題も浮き彫りになった）\n（新人にしては上手だが面白みが少ない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(They both had a good start‚ but a distinct problem has recently taken shape.)\n(Though they’re talented for newcomers‚ they’re not that interesting.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.103333377838135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（『長瀬麻奈の妹』を観に来ているだけ……辛辣だが）\n（琴乃達がクリアしなければならない課題だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(“They’re only coming to watch Mana Nagase’s little sister”… is a harsh statement‚)\n(but it’s an obstacle Kotono and the others will have to clear.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.98830588658651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、そこでストップ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ pause right there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.757960616678435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "伊吹さん、リズムもタイミングもバッチリよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ your rhythm and timing are spot-on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.524627283345104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ ma’am!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.50916250063026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でもここはあなたが一番前に出るパートよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is the part where you’re supposed to be the most in front.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.018051460514904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もっと自信を持って、心持ち大きめに動かないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to have more confidence and dance with a bit more presence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.132871559391866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "自信……\n……はいっ、分かりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Confidence…\nYes‚ ma’am! I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.778324680940464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ少し休憩にしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ ladies‚ let’s take a little break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.14499134760713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃん、凄く頑張ってますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ you’ve really been working hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.23140854578829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "今回の振りつけ、結構難しい動きが多いのに\nもうリズムもタイミングもバッチリだなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography for this song has so many tricky sections‚\nyet your rhythm and timing are spot-on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.82873269460219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もまだちょっと覚え切れてないなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m having a hard time memorizing it all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.75741748553134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、みんなありがとう\nもっと自信持てって言われちゃったけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Thanks‚ everyone.\nThough she did say‚ I needed a little more confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.11304534019649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "自信を持つことは大切ですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having self-confidence is indeed quite important!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.55392532091955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "渚も、私のこの堂々とした立ち居振る舞いを\n見習うといいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa‚ I suggest you pay close attention to the bold way in which I carry myself\nand emulate what you see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.23220190745212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "堂々とするのはいいけど\nすずはまず立ち位置をしっかり頭に入れておいてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being bold is nice and all‚ Suzu‚\nbut first‚ you’d better memorize your place in the formations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.16553524078547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "さっき思いっきりぶつかってたもんねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you collided epically with her earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.37209668650786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……\nそう、たまたまですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I…\nRight! It was a mere coincidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.25055472547373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（俺にはそんな彼女達に報告することがあった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I have an announcement to make to them.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.41722139214039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 91.08388805880708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今回のグランプリは三年ぶりの開催だ。それに伴って\n特別に予選が開かれることになるそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This Grand Prix will be the first in three years. Because of that‚\nthey’re going to hold a special preliminary round.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.32980650757308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "予選？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preliminary round?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.99647317423975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is the meaning of this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.19647317423976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリの休止期間中、挑戦出来なかった\nアイドルもいるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While the Grand Prix was on hiatus‚ there were many idols\nwho were unable to compete‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.66313979322275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だから今回に限り、活動期間が六年以内のアイドルに\nグランプリの参加資格が与えられることになったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So just this year‚ idols who’ve been active within the past six years\nwill be allowed to compete.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.09647312655608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ハードルが高いなんて、初めから分かってる\nそんなことで尻込みしてる場合じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve known from the very start that the bar was set high.\nNow’s not the time to balk at the challenge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.15590626890024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ\n元より、私達が目指すのは頂点だけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But of course.\nAll along‚ our only goal has been the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.55590626890024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "いくら数が増えようが\nその全てをなぎ倒せばいいだけのこと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we have to compete against more and more idols‚\nthen we need only topple them all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1892396022336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんが全てを力尽くで\n――でりゃああっ、と？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you mean‚ Suzu-nyan‚ that you’d physically\ntackle them all to the ground?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.18923960223376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "パフォーマンスでです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll tackle them with my performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3225729355671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "それはともかく、経験を積んだアイドルも\n大勢出場するということですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nevertheless‚ this means that well-seasoned idols\nwill also be in the competition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.13869542772161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "なら、練習の密度をさらに\n上げていく必要があるでしょう",
      "translations": {
